title: Microsoft Office 2010 VL ProPlus English (x86-x64) April 2016
description:
Release Info

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Products Version: 14.0.7166.5000 SP2
- Architectures: x86/x64
- Integrated updates: April 12, 2016
- Spelling tools: English, French, Spanish

OS Requirements

- Windows XP with SP3 (excluding 64-bit editions)
- Windows Vista SP1 / 7 / 8 /10
- Windows Server 2003 with SP2 and MSXML 6.0 (excluding 64-bit edition)
- Windows Server 2003 R2 / 2008 / 2008 R2 / 2012

Includes

- Microsoft Office Professional Plus (Volume License)
- Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (activator - bonus folder)
- Optional: Classic Menu for Office v5.85, Office Tab v9.81 (bonus folder)

Installation

- Mount / burn / extract and run Setup
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (bonus folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)
